# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sensitive — must never be committed (esp. to a public repo)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google OAuth "Desktop app" client — distribute in the release zip, not in git.
credentials.json
# Per-user settings (player name, path overrides, selected worlds).
settings.json
# Cached OAuth token store (normally in %APPDATA%\ValheimSync\token; guard local copies too).
token/
*.token
# Local machine-specific Claude Code settings.
.claude/settings.local.json

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build output / publish artifacts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
bin/
obj/
# Published single-file exe lives here alongside copies of credentials/settings — never commit it.
publish/
[Pp]ublish/
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
# First-time-install zips built by scripts/release.ps1 (the bundled exe + credentials are
# already ignored above). The setup guide dist/SETUP.md IS tracked.
dist/*.zip
dist/.stage/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# World save backups the app creates
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.synbak
# Temp exe swaps left by the auto-updater.
*.exe.old
*.exe.new

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IDE / editor
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS cruft
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
